        <!-- PAGE 1: COVER & EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
        <div class="page">
            <div class="document-header">
                <div class="header-left">
                    <h1>System Charter v4.0</h1>
                    <div class="subtitle">Spectrum Application Transformation Charter</div>
                </div>
                <div class="header-right">
                    <div class="adobe-logo">Adobe</div>
                    <div class="document-meta">
                        <strong>Version:</strong> 4.0<br>
                        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> September 29, 2025<br>
                        <strong>Charter Owner:</strong> Design System Lead<br>
                        <span class="status-badge">Pending Approval</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
            
            <div class="callout highlight">
                <div class="callout-title">Strategic Transformation</div>
                <p>Adobe is transforming Spectrum from a static documentation system into the <strong>Spectrum application</strong>—a fully realized, living product that unifies design system resources across all platforms.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>The Spectrum app is powered by Adobe's implementation of <strong>Knapsack</strong> and the <strong>Intelligent Product Engine (IPE)</strong>, enabling multi-platform design system delivery with AI-powered automation.</p>
            
            <p>This charter replaces the prior infrastructure-only approach with a <strong>product-centric design system strategy</strong>, ensuring Spectrum becomes a dependable, authoritative interface for all Adobe design system users.</p>
            
            <h3>Financial Summary</h3>
            <div class="metrics-grid">
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">$945K</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Annual Value</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">530%</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Net ROI</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value">3.4 mo</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">Payback Period</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>2. Business Objectives</h2>
            
            <h3>Primary Objectives</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Deliver the <strong>Spectrum app</strong> as the unified, authoritative interface for Adobe's design system across platforms</li>
                <li>Launch <strong>Spectrum 2</strong> with integrated guidance, tokens, accessibility principles, and multi-platform system behaviors</li>
                <li>Provide <strong>single-source-of-truth documentation</strong>, reducing drift between design and code</li>
                <li>Enable <strong>partner access parity</strong>, ensuring internal and external teams use the same system</li>
                <li>Automate multi-platform governance via IPE for faster, safer component evolution</li>
                <li>Reduce operational overhead through design-to-code automation, drift detection, and contributor workflow tooling</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="page-footer">
                <span>Adobe Confidential — System Charter v4.0</span>
                <span>Page 1 of 5</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
