            <h2>3. Scope & Boundaries</h2>
            
            <div class="two-column">
                <div>
                    <h3>In Scope</h3>
                    
                    <h4>Spectrum Application Platform</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Development and launch of the Spectrum app as a product</li>
                        <li>Integration of design, code, tokens, guidelines, examples, and workflows</li>
                        <li>Multi-platform view (Web, iOS, Android, desktop)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>AI Workflow Integration (IPE)</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Drift detection</li>
                        <li>Automated accessibility validation</li>
                        <li>Migration planning</li>
                        <li>Component deduplication</li>
                        <li>System-aware code generation</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Partner Ecosystem Enablement</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Partner access parity</li>
                        <li>Contribution workflow standardization</li>
                        <li>Shared governance for system evolution</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h3>Out of Scope (Phase 1)</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Non-Spectrum app Adobe Creative Cloud integrations</li>
                        <li>Multi-brand design systems (future phase)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="callout">
                        <div class="callout-title">Phase 2 Considerations</div>
                        <p>Multi-brand architecture and extended Creative Cloud integrations will be evaluated following successful Phase 1 deployment and adoption validation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
