        <div class="page">
            <div class="section-label">Governance & Workstreams</div>
            <h2>4. Governance Structure</h2>
            
            <div class="two-column">
                <div>
                    <h3>Steering Committee</h3>
                    <p>Provides strategic oversight, funding, risk resolution, and approval of major direction changes.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Spectrum App Product Board <span class="status-badge">New</span></h3>
                    <p>Provides product governance for the Spectrum application.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Members</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Senior Director, Experience Design (Spectrum)</li>
                        <li>Design System Lead</li>
                        <li>Spectrum App Product Manager</li>
                        <li>Engineering Platform Lead</li>
                        <li>Accessibility Lead</li>
                        <li>CX Partner (Knapsack)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Responsibilities</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Prioritize Spectrum app roadmap</li>
                        <li>Manage contribution lifecycle</li>
                        <li>Ensure accessibility, consistency, and multi-platform integrity</li>
                        <li>Oversee release cycles and governance compliance</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h3>Core Implementation Team</h3>
                    <p>Executes implementation of the Spectrum app and IPE integration.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Extended Teams</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Designers (system + product teams)</li>
                        <li>Engineers (Web, React, iOS, Android)</li>
                        <li>Accessibility specialists</li>
                        <li>Implementation Partner Council</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>5. Workstreams</h2>
            
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%;">Workstream</th>
                    <th>Key Deliverables</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>1. Spectrum App Platform Foundation</strong></td>
                    <td>Build infrastructure on Knapsack; Adobe IAM integration; Token management; Unified component catalog; Enterprise security guidelines</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>2. IPE Integration</strong></td>
                    <td>Drift detection; Migration planning for Spectrum 2; Contribution workflow acceleration; Accessible component validation</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>3. Partner Enablement</strong></td>
                    <td>Partner onboarding; Shared access; Contribution pathways; Training program for internal + external teams</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>4. Governance & Quality</strong></td>
                    <td>Component lifecycle management; Automated governance via IPE; Release notes and versioning structure</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>5. Measurement & Analytics</strong></td>
                    <td>App engagement analytics; Drift index; Contribution pipeline analytics; Partner usage telemetry</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>6. Spectrum App Productization</strong> <span class="status-badge">New</span></td>
                    <td>App MVP delivery; Contributor dashboard; Component validation tooling; Release management and roadmap cadence</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            
